venue_partners.about: Ramanujan college is a premier institution of the University of Delhi and has been accredited grade `A` by the National Assessment and Accreditation Council (NAAC). We at Ramanujan College emphasize on the holistic development of personality and meaningful exposure to real world and in the process attain excellence. In this endeavour to organise a value packed Global FinTech Conference, Department of Commerce, Computer Science and Management Studies of Ramanujan College have locked their synergies together.
